---
title: "Dynamic: Change Critical Flag"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Organization Admin
    participant UI as UI Components
    participant DataSvc as AccessIntelligenceDataService
    participant PersistSvc as ReportPersistenceService
    participant Server as Bitwarden Server

    Admin->>UI: Mark/Unmark application as critical

    alt Mark as critical
        UI->>DataSvc: markApplicationsAsCritical$(names)
        DataSvc->>DataSvc: report.markApplicationAsCritical(name)
        Note over DataSvc: View model mutation — no report regeneration<br/>report.recomputeSummary()
    else Unmark as critical
        UI->>DataSvc: unmarkApplicationsAsCritical$(names)
        DataSvc->>DataSvc: report.unmarkApplicationAsCritical(name)
        Note over DataSvc: View model mutation — no report regeneration<br/>report.recomputeSummary()
    end

    DataSvc-->>UI: report$ emits (same reference, flag updated)
    Note over UI: UI reflects updated critical status immediately

    DataSvc->>PersistSvc: saveApplicationMetadata$(report)
    Note over PersistSvc: Settings only — critical flags + review dates<br/>No encryption needed (metadata stored in DB)
    PersistSvc->>Server: updateRiskInsightsApplicationData$() via RiskInsightsApiService
    Server-->>PersistSvc: success
